fixed_skill.name: Spirit Binding

innate_skill.desc: At the start of battle, increase Attack by 12.1% for 2 turns.
innate_skill.name: Attack Master II

innate_skill.name: Dormina

passive_skill.desc: Increase critical damage by 15%. When attacking a foe with a debuff, increase Attack by 30%. If damage is dealt, increase party's Attack by 10% for 1 turn.
passive_skill.name: Bloodthirsty Warrior

passive_skill.desc: Increase critical damage by 15%. When attacking a foe with a debuff, increase Attack by 35%. If damage is dealt, increase party's Attack by 11.5% for 1 turn.

showtime_skill.desc: Deal Physical damage to all foes equal to 180.0%/192.6%/205.2% of Attack.
